---
// src/pages/sponsor.astro
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="light">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Sponsor & Advertise – DesignTechNews</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Reach 12,000+ designers, developers, and tech professionals across Africa and the world. Sponsor DesignTechNews newsletter, listings, and more." />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Sponsor DesignTechNews – Reach Africa's Design & Tech Audience" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Promote your product, job, or program to 12,000+ monthly readers across Africa and beyond." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png" />
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png" />
  <link rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest" />

  <!-- Google Analytics 4 -->
  <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-XLJSZNT4HL"></script>
  <script is:inline>
    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
    function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
    gtag('js', new Date());
    gtag('config', 'G-XLJSZNT4HL');
  </script>

  <style>
    /* ── Hero ── */
    .sponsor-hero {
      padding: 96px 0 80px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .sponsor-hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -200px; left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 800px; height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(37,99,235,0.08) 0%, transparent 65%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .sponsor-hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -100px; right: -100px;
      width: 400px; height: 400px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(34,197,94,0.06) 0%, transparent 65%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .sponsor-hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -2px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      max-width: 780px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
    }

    .sponsor-hero h1 em {
      font-style: normal;
      color: var(--blue);
    }

    .sponsor-hero p {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto 40px;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .hero-cta-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    /* ── Audience stats bar ── */
    .stats-bar {
      background: var(--navy);
      padding: 36px 0;
    }

    .stats-bar-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .stat-item {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0 48px;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .stat-item:last-child { border-right: none; }

    .stat-item .num {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: white;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .stat-item .num span { color: var(--green); }

    .stat-item .label {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      font-weight: 500;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* ── Why sponsor ── */
    .why-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .why-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 28px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .why-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(37,99,235,0.2);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    .why-icon {
      width: 44px; height: 44px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .why-icon.blue   { background: rgba(37,99,235,0.1); }
    .why-icon.green  { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.1); }
    .why-icon.amber  { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.1); }
    .why-icon.purple { background: rgba(124,58,237,0.1); }

    .why-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .why-card p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* ── Packages ── */
    .packages-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .package-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 32px;
      position: relative;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .package-card:hover {
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .package-card.featured {
      border-color: var(--blue);
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(37,99,235,0.04) 0%, var(--bg-card) 60%);
    }

    .package-card.featured::before {
      content: 'Most Popular';
      position: absolute;
      top: -12px; left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: var(--blue);
      color: white;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 4px 14px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .package-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .badge-starter  { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.1);  color: var(--green-dark); }
    .badge-growth   { background: rgba(37,99,235,0.1);  color: var(--blue); }
    .badge-premium  { background: rgba(124,58,237,0.1); color: #7C3AED; }
    .badge-custom   { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.1); color: #D97706; }

    [data-theme="dark"] .badge-starter { color: var(--green); }

    .package-name {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .package-desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .package-price {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .price-amount {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -1.5px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .price-period {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .price-note {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .package-divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .package-features {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .package-features li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .feat-check {
      width: 18px; height: 18px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(34,197,94,0.12);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: var(--green-dark);
    }

    [data-theme="dark"] .feat-check { color: var(--green); }

    .package-cta {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 13px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      text-align: center;
      display: block;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .cta-primary {
      background: var(--blue);
      color: white;
      border: none;
    }

    .cta-primary:hover {
      background: var(--blue-dark);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(37,99,235,0.35);
    }

    .cta-outline {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border-dark);
    }

    .cta-outline:hover {
      border-color: var(--blue);
      color: var(--blue);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    /* ── Process ── */
    .process-steps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 0;
      margin-top: 48px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .process-steps::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 28px; left: 10%; right: 10%;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
    }

    .process-step {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 20px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .step-num {
      width: 56px; height: 56px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--blue);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .process-step:hover .step-num {
      border-color: var(--blue);
      background: rgba(37,99,235,0.06);
    }

    .process-step h4 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .process-step p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Contact form ── */
    .sponsor-form-section {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .sponsor-form-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    }

    .form-sidebar {
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--navy) 0%, #0F2256 60%, #0D3B2E 100%);
      padding: 48px 40px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .form-sidebar::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -80px; right: -80px;
      width: 300px; height: 300px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(37,99,235,0.25) 0%, transparent 65%);
    }

    .form-sidebar::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -60px; left: -40px;
      width: 250px; height: 250px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(34,197,94,0.15) 0%, transparent 65%);
    }

    .form-sidebar-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

    .form-sidebar h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: white;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .form-sidebar p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .sidebar-contact-list {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .sidebar-contact-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    }

    .sidebar-contact-list .icon {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 16px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .sidebar-contact-list a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .sidebar-contact-list a:hover { color: white; }

    .form-main { padding: 48px 40px; }

    .form-main h3 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .form-main .form-sub {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .form-group input,
    .form-group select,
    .form-group textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 11px 14px;
      background: var(--bg);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text);
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .form-group input:focus,
    .form-group select:focus,
    .form-group textarea:focus { border-color: var(--blue); }

    .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 100px; }

    .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }

    .form-submit-btn {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px;
      background: var(--blue);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .form-submit-btn:hover {
      background: var(--blue-dark);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(37,99,235,0.35);
    }

    .form-submit-btn:disabled {
      opacity: 0.6;
      cursor: not-allowed;
      transform: none;
    }

    .form-success {
      display: none;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .form-success h4 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .form-success p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 360px;
    }

    /* ── FAQ ── */
    .faq-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
      margin-top: 40px;
      max-width: 720px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .faq-item {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .faq-item:hover { border-color: rgba(37,99,235,0.2); }

    .faq-question {
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 18px 22px;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      cursor: pointer;
      text-align: left;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .faq-arrow {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      transition: transform 0.25s;
    }

    .faq-item.open .faq-arrow { transform: rotate(180deg); }

    .faq-answer {
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height 0.3s ease, padding 0.3s ease;
    }

    .faq-item.open .faq-answer { max-height: 300px; }

    .faq-answer-inner {
      padding: 0 22px 18px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .sponsor-form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .form-sidebar { padding: 36px 28px; }
      .form-main { padding: 36px 28px; }
      .process-steps::before { display: none; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .stat-item { padding: 16px 24px; border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
      .stat-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
      .stats-bar-inner { flex-direction: column; }
      .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .sponsor-hero { padding: 64px 0 56px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- MOBILE NAV -->
<nav class="mobile-nav" id="mobileNav" role="navigation" aria-label="Mobile navigation">
  <button class="mobile-close" id="mobileClose" aria-label="Close menu">✕</button>
  <a href="/">Home</a>
  <a href="/opportunities">Opportunities</a>
  <a href="/jobs">Jobs</a>
  <a href="/news">News</a>
  <a href="/about">About</a>
</nav>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header>
  <div class="container">
    <nav>
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <img src="/images/light-logo.png" alt="DesignTechNews" class="logo-img logo-light" />
        <img src="/images/dark-logo.png" alt="DesignTechNews" class="logo-img logo-dark" />
      </a>
      <ul class="nav-links" role="list">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/opportunities">Opportunities</a></li>
        <li><a href="/jobs">Jobs</a></li>
        <li><a href="/news">News</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="nav-right">
        <button class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle" aria-label="Toggle dark mode">🌙</button>
        <a href="#contact-form" class="btn-subscribe">Get a Sponsor Slot</a>
        <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger" aria-label="Open menu">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<main>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="sponsor-hero">
    <div class="container">
      
      <span class="hero-badge" style="display:inline-flex;margin-bottom:28px;">📢 Advertising & Sponsorship</span>
      <h1>Reach <em>Africa's Most Engaged</em><br>Design & Tech Audience</h1>
      <p>Put your brand, job opening, or program in front of 12,000+ designers, developers, and creative professionals who are actively looking to grow.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta-row">
        <a href="#packages" class="btn-primary">View Packages →</a>
        <a href="#contact-form" class="btn-secondary">Talk to Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS BAR -->
  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats-bar-inner">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <p class="num">12<span>K+</span></p>
          <p class="label">Monthly Readers</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <p class="num">50<span>+</span></p>
          <p class="label">Countries Reached</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <p class="num">200<span>+</span></p>
          <p class="label">Active Opportunities</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <p class="num">48<span>%</span></p>
          <p class="label">Africa-Based Audience</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <p class="num">62<span>%</span></p>
          <p class="label">Email Open Rate</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- WHY SPONSOR -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">🎯 Why Sponsor</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">An audience that's ready to act</h2>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon blue">🎨</div>
          <h3>Design & Tech Professionals</h3>
          <p>Our readers are designers, developers, and product builders — not passive scrollers. They're actively looking for tools, opportunities, and jobs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon green">🌍</div>
          <h3>Africa-First, Globally Minded</h3>
          <p>Tap into Africa's fastest-growing tech talent pool while reaching an international audience that cares about the continent's ecosystem.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon amber">📬</div>
          <h3>High-Intent Newsletter Readers</h3>
          <p>Our subscribers opted in specifically for opportunities and resources. They're the most receptive audience you can reach in this niche.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon purple">💡</div>
          <h3>Trusted Editorial Context</h3>
          <p>Sponsorships appear alongside hand-curated content — not banner ads. Your brand benefits from being associated with quality and relevance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PACKAGES -->
  <section class="bg-subtle" id="packages">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">💼 Packages</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Choose your sponsorship</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:8px;max-width:520px;">All prices are introductory rates. Early sponsors get the best pricing and first pick of slots.</p>

      <div class="packages-grid">

        <!-- Starter -->
        <div class="package-card">
          <span class="package-badge badge-starter">Starter</span>
          <h3 class="package-name">Featured Listing</h3>
          <p class="package-desc">Get your job or opportunity pinned at the top of a relevant section for maximum visibility.</p>
          <div class="package-price">
            <span class="price-amount">$49</span>
            <span class="price-period">/ listing</span>
          </div>
          <p class="price-note">One-time · No commitment</p>
